		(descr "CRSF / ELRS RX solder-pad array (4 pads: 5V/TX/RX/GND). 1.5x2.0mm SMD pads at 2.5mm pitch in a row. Replaces JST-GH 4P (master Phase 4b option-θ — 4× MP-pad JST-GH on 36×36 over-constrained; CRSF is the connector most amenable to solder-pad termination since ELRS RX is semi-permanently installed). Pin convention matches Phase 3g crsf_usb_3g.py: pin 1=+5V, pin 2=USART6_TX, pin 3=USART6_RX, pin 4=GND.")
